Challange:Create and share a file
->Create a text file
->Ensure any user can read and write it
->Compress the file using tar or zip

SOLUTION:
1.To create a file:
vi newfile
2.To ensure user can read and write it:
chmod a+rw newfile
3.Compress the file using tar or zip:
tar -czf newfile.tgz.newfile-->To put in archive
ls -lh newfile.tgz
